# The movement to the iron ore position was successful. Now, I will proceed to harvest some iron ore.
# I will aim to gather a quantity of 10 iron ore to start with, similar to what I did with the coal.

iron_quantity_to_harvest = 10
harvested_iron = harvest_resource(iron_position, quantity=iron_quantity_to_harvest)  # Harvest the iron ore
print(f'Harvested iron quantity: {harvested_iron}')  # Check how much iron was harvested
print(f"Inventory changed to {inspect_inventory()}")  # Check the updated inventory after harvesting iron ore
